Changes and additions in this distribution (Tom Smart / SmartFlow Observatory, 2026):
  - attribution-ref-extension.md -- spec draft generalising the attribution
    envelope over typed subject positions [endpoint, address(payTo), key(operator)]
    at fixed arity three, with the observation bound on the endpoint member.
  - attribution_ref_v1.json -- positive and negative conformance vectors, computed
    independently against the upstream pin.
  - runner_python.py, runner_node.js -- two independent RFC 8785 (JCS) + SHA-256
    verifiers.
  - observations/ -- live HTTP 402 observations used as drift-versus-tamper vectors.

The upstream canonicalisation pin and its discipline are referenced unchanged; no
upstream files are modified or redistributed in this repository.
